1
{
  name { The trash dump }
  desc {
"   You are standing knee-deep in a pile of assorted debris, cardboard-
like scraps and needle-like bits of bent metal. The room is in fact a
part of a curving corridor, going east and south.
  }
  extra {
	keywords { debris junk cardboard needle" }
	desc { It is obviously totally useless, even if you do not understand what it
actually is.
	}
	keywords { hole" }
	desc { It appears to be changing shape continually, widening and narrowing,
though never quite closing.
	}
  }
  flags { dark, indoors }
  exits {
	to { e, 2 }
	  desc { The corridor continues turning right as long as your light reaches. It
looks cleaner that way.
}
	to { s, 3 }
	  desc { The corridor continues turning left as long as you can see. There are
no more debris a short stretch down this corridor.
}
	to { u, Main_matrix:10 }
	  desc { There is a small hole high above you, barely reachable from the top of
the largest pile of trash.
}
  }
}

